We solved this problem with <a href=\https://github.com/polleverywhere/sprockets_bower" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/polleverywhere/sprockets_bower</a> in a simpler way.<p>This reminds me that bundler could handle dependency resolution beyond gems. Imagine:<p><pre><code>  gem &quot;rails&quot;
